{"tid":367442,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"俾你揀多次 你會番intern定做自己想做嘅野","createTime":"2017-08-20T17:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T04:54:43.000Z","uid":75373,"like":24,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a71d1a3b25d5a57b141904191285867df7b59080","tid":367442,"uid":75373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:11:22.000Z","msg":"下年summer係最後一個summer<br />\n見到大我一年嘅人好多今年都番曬intern<br />\n但我覺得最後一個暑假好似應該好好珍惜<br />\n做自己想做嘅野先<br />\n旅行又好 為興趣愛好學野又好 周圍見識又好<br />\n但好似如果唔番intern<br />\n同其他人好似爭左D野 少左競爭力咁<br />\n<br />\n如果俾你揀多次<br />\n你會寧願選擇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟隨自己個心 做自己想做嘅野 浪費青春<br />\n定<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 番intern 充實自己裝備自己 人人有嘅野你都要有"},{"pid":"9594e5a8c6dbc8cd5cc2a1ccf522cefcb54ce3b3","tid":367442,"uid":135368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:33:30.000Z","msg":"做自己想做既野唔一定係浪費青春"},{"pid":"87eaa7b5e7c03043e707f3b972f0bcc330de4c15","tid":367442,"uid":15129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:36:49.000Z","msg":"啲朋友返intern日日呻扮工<br />\n屌 心諗咁你又返 留返啲時間做自己想做嘅嘢仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099454f57c8262d8875dfef19e7feef2f805e8d1","tid":367442,"uid":75373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:39:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做自己想做既野唔一定係浪費青春</blockquote><br />\n如果你不曾浪費青春 那就是在浪費青春<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n純粹咁諗"},{"pid":"77758704bbf99fdd955e955b4409dc803a668447","tid":367442,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:40:52.000Z","msg":"下年year4<br />\n0 intern<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f043ffcba1c60a9a497550218fdb019d27ffef5","tid":367442,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T17:42:14.000Z","msg":"做自己既野，有時收穫仲大<br />\n<br />\n未返過summer intern<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（雖然返過winter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"0939e892910c85cf130b0b917057cd838de38818","tid":367442,"uid":54946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:03:59.000Z","msg":"返緊intern<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 終於明白浪費青春既重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bfd4fd22711b6421df885a36b86532453e7a2f5","tid":367442,"uid":111596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T03:32:20.000Z","msg":"如果唔係GRAD要求一定唔會做.<br />\n仲要係LOW PAY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都要多謝份INTERN比我知道我將來搵工一定唔會係依類工."},{"pid":"15ef5f01e5fdf4e0bf103a366518a56a5e09a39a","tid":367442,"uid":134988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T04:37:34.000Z","msg":"最慘係d intern 做完搵工無幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73d7d52cffccd85357a70927ec07e809791d711","tid":367442,"uid":139993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T04:54:43.000Z","msg":"在polyu，好似無都揀<br />\n唔返intern=無都grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}